<h2 class="bold font-l">MGS3: Snake Eater</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
This Secret Theatre scene (called &quot;The Ultimate Weapon&quot;) has Snake and The Boss engage in a casual game of Rock-Paper Scissors. Things quickly go awry when... wait... why does she have a gun?! </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MundaneMadeAwesome" class='trope-example-link'>Mundane Made Awesome</a></p>
</div>
