<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">MGS3: Snake Eater</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
This Secret Theatre scene (called &quot;The Ultimate Weapon&quot;) has Snake and The Boss engage in a casual game of Rock-Paper Scissors. Things quickly go awry when... wait... why does she have a gun?!	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="q7uwxt">
